<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Richmond</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">One of Calgary’s oldest and popular established residential neighborhoods, Richmond is spread out on both sides of the Crowchild Trail in South West Calgary. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Originally a location for the famous Alberta Children’s Hospital, the community replaced the hospital facility after it was moved to NW Calgary in 2007.</p>
            <p class="par-xl">Located within the close vicinity of the community, Marda Loop offers endless recreational opportunities to the residents in the form of restaurants, cafes and shopping stores.</p>
        </div>
